item.title: Blogtober Tech Edition 2020
item.description: I hit my first anniversary of blogging this past September. As you may have noticed, I’ve been a bit lax over the main course of this year. I know, I know. With the whole COVID thing going on this year, you would have thought there would have been more time to blog.
